# Seed index constituent files live here.
#
# Populated by `python scripts/fetch_seed_indices.py` from the repo root
# before the first build. Each file has the shape:
#   { "alias": "NIFTY_50", "last_updated": "YYYY-MM-DD", "symbols": [...] }
#
# The empty seed is sufficient to keep the app booting; the Tauri host
# spawns a background refresh on startup that will fill these in.
